    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just trying to understand what the actual risk is. i've heard people mix stuff all the time and it's fine. is there a specific reason why these two shouldn't be taken together, or is it just one of those things where doctors are extra cautious for no reason? i really need to know if it's like, 'call an ambulance' dangerous or just 'might feel a bit nauseous' dangerous.",
